window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>New York Times</i> best-selling author Simon R. Green creates a fantastical world in his <i>Secret Histories</i> series, in which the Drood family protects mankind from creatures of the night.</p><p> Eddie Drood is not happy about being the new head of the family, especially now that everyone believes either he or his girlfriend, Molly, was responsible for the former matriarch’s death. Since Eddie knows he didn’t do it, he doesn’t like where this is going.</p>"; 
